Our Team 






PartnersSuzanne Shank is the Chairwoman, CEO, founding owner and majority stakeholder of Siebert Cisneros Shank & Co., L.L.C.  Additional stakeholders are Henry Cisneros, Chairman of the Executive Committee and Principal, William Thompson, Jr., Chief Administrative Officer, Gary Hall, National Head of Investment Banking, Victor Miramontes, and Sean Duffy, Managing Director, Head of Institutional Sales.

Banking TeamThe Siebert Cisneros Shank banking team is made up of the brightest, most creative and experienced bankers in the industry with the specialty focus and skill sets to guide our clients through successful transactions. Our collaborative approach pools diverse knowledge and perspectives to produce results far beyond expectations
